{"id":284676,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-上海维权人士孙洪琴拘留期满获释（图）/","date":"2013-03-18T17:31:38Z","modified":"2013-03-19T18:19:44Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士孙洪琴拘留期满获释（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日上午</span><span>，因欲向两会代表递交提议而遭到行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天的上海维权人士孙洪琴，从闸北区拘留所获释回到家中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，孙洪琴，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">59</span><span>岁，住上海闸北区京市江路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">64</span><span>号，原上海大隆机器厂一名女职工。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>年前孙洪琴遭受法院枉法判决，造成家破子散。由于官官相护司法腐败，想讨回公道反被拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>多天、多次被关黑监狱、被殴打、被精神病司法鉴定。唯一生活来源的养老金被上海市长宁区法院无任何法律手续冻结至今</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月房子又被贱价强征，上海市房地局篡改房产档案，诉讼法院不立案。孙洪琴至今一无所有。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>这次被上海公安拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，从上海市公安局开给孙洪琴的行政拘留决定书来看，说是现已查明孙洪琴于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分</span><span>在天安门地区扰乱公共场所秩序，根据《中华人民共和国治安管理处罚法》之规定，决定处以孙洪琴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天行政拘留的行政处罚，从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日结束。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>对此，孙洪琴表示：这分明是滥用司法，也是上海当局打击报复上海维权上访人士的常用手法，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日下午</span><span>，她只是去人民大会堂准备向全国两会代表递交提议。如果这也叫“扰乱公共场所秩序”？那么，这个社会就是颠倒黑白，乌云黑天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>孙洪琴联系电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18939958679</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-gBsnFZtpnqM/UUc9-sdk3FI/AAAAAAAAe-E/0aTD6ZTodjA/s1600/%E5%AD%99%E6%B4%AA%E7%90%B4_163820.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-gBsnFZtpnqM/UUc9-sdk3FI/AAAAAAAAe-E/0aTD6ZTodjA/s320/%E5%AD%99%E6%B4%AA%E7%90%B4_163820.jpg\" width=\"225\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,1],"tags":[]}